307
00:17:20,312 --> 00:17:22,312
Kalau begitu...

308
00:17:33,812 --> 00:17:35,612
Apa yang kau lakukan, Conan?

309
00:17:35,612 --> 00:17:38,012
Kau memberi tanda di dinding.

310
